00:10.210 --> 00:15.550
but somehow we end up with software that is difficult to scale and to maintain.

00:15.910 --> 00:23.230
It said that we don't rise to the level of our expectations, but instead we fall to the level of our

00:23.230 --> 00:23.760
training.

