00:48.970 --> 00:55.870
Watch the videos as well as doing the quizzes and the assignments in the moments the course calls for

00:55.870 --> 00:56.070
it.

00:56.080 --> 01:01.840
Download the source code, follow along and play with the code experiment.

01:01.840 --> 01:06.940
